title: Garena to Oceania Transfer
body:
So my friend has an account in Garena but she wants to transfer to Oceania. I googled it and it says registration is closed.
Is there any way to transfer from Garena to Oceania now or what?

replies.body: I have no idea on the matter. I, for one, thought it was possible for anyone to transfer to anywhere, as long as they had enough RP.
